Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.19,0:00:06.00,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The Britannian youth, Lelouch, obtained two powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:08.18,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,One of them is Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:11.97,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to give an order to anyone. A power that enforces absolute obedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.29,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The other is the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:19.45,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,His personal army formed to destroy the Britannia Empire, ruled by his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:23.58,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch has started to act by using the code name "Zero"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:30.71,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,in order to avenge his mother and turn the world into a place that his sister, Nunnally, can live happily in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.81,0:00:35.03,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,What kinds of results will those actions bring?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:38.01,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, no one knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:27.59,Default,TV,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that reconstruction work has finally begun at the Kawaguchiko Convention Center Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:30.70,Default,TV02,0000,0000,0000,,It's been more than two weeks since Zero unveiled the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:33.34,Default,TV02,0000,0000,0000,,However, actual evidence has yet to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:35.82,Default,TV01,0000,0000,0000,,Did they conceal their escape route?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:39.03,Default,TV01,0000,0000,0000,,They freed the hostages and escaped on the main coastal road...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:51.57,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Kallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:53.07,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:55.07,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for waking you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:56.23,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:59.37,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. This time it's because the ladder fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:02.90,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and clean this up. It's almost time for me to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:06.65,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress, you've been going to school more often lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:07.54,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make any friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:09.48,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your concern, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:15.34,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Go away, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:28.51,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they said it's for social security, it's such a waste to give this to the Elevens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:30.86,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it ended up with you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:33.65,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it {\b1}is{\b0} better that the population of the Elevens shrinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:38.15,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,I'll transfer the money to your wife's account.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:42.64,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness Cornelia is a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:45.07,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,She won't accept these kinds of acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:50.33,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Lights! Turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:56.17,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You guys are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.40,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,The Order of the Black Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:09.09,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,That's so unlike you, Kallen! Falling asleep like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:10.93,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I was a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:15.48,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you become Lelouch's disciple? That guy is an expert at sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.01,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.02,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,That's him sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:23.28,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what he does every night, but he slept through more than half of the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:29.19,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,A battle has broken out against the EU at the El Alamein Front.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:34.33,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,This means that we can't always be held up by Area 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.46,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,We need to deal with our domestic affairs and turn this into a safe area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:41.31,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,In order to do that, it's urgent to eliminate terrorist organizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:46.01,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,But the drug "Refrain", which is widespread among the the Elevens, is an urgent matter as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:48.22,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Productivity has dropped because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:52.33,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,We must terminate the main transportation route to the Chinese Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:53.64,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.56,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:58.11,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,You too. Stop going to the settlements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:05:01.02,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, about the Order of the Black Knights...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:05.50,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let them roam free for a while, since I owe them a favor for saving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:07.90,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,However, when I return...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:17.54,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I shall clean up this Area before handing it to you, so please don't think of anything dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.07,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Euphie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:25.37,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Because that man was a child of the Emperor of Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:25.79,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:27.29,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.22,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You are one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:33.06,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:37.32,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,The significance of Zero's words at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:39.46,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Do they mean that he's going to continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:44.68,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, how would you feel about Zero's actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.32,Default,Eupehmia,0000,0000,0000,,And about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:55.35,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Living two lives is tiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:57.19,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Suzaku! Over there! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.92,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, stop it, Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.02,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:03.33,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Lelouch, but it's an order from the President...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:05.74,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You're smiling! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:06.76,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Stop moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:09.38,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Morning-nya~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:11.22,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Good... mor... ning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.46,0:06:13.77,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,What's that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:15.39,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? No one told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.21,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,It's Arthur's welcome party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.27,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,It seems peaceful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.45,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Let's enjoy ourselves while the other activities have been suspended.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.40,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Kallen, I've prepared some costumes for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:24.81,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:27.39,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,It's an apology for saying those strange things to you the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:28.31,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Which one will you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:29.70,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.28,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Kallen doesn't need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:31.79,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:34.12,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,She's already put on a special outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:37.46,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go on television?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:38.75,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:40.96,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,How was it, Miss Television Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.33,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the topic has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:46.92,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Quit joking about that. It was really tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:52.01,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,We're constantly surrounded and questioned by people, even in the bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:55.68,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even get out of school this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:59.81,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,So why are we prohibited from going outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:01.62,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,It's the thing called friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:06.70,Note,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Milly is quoting a line from the Japanese version of Romance of the Three\NKingdoms. We've used a translation that's closer to the original Chinese version.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:03.82,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,"We were not able to be born on the same year, same month, and same day,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:06.70,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,but we hope to die on the same year, same month, and same day." --Romance of the Three Kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.35,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:10.53,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,It means that even in death-nya~, drag people down with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:13.16,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty mean, isn't she, Suzaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:15.04,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:15.52,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:18.37,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,For all of us to be together again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.25,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,This is really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:22.50,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong-nya~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.39,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,We should be laughing now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:29.29,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the nice thing about Suzaku-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:32.01,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to say, "Take the atmosphere into consideration," from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:33.93,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.69,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, it's just a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:40.06,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I saved everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:44.60,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since our grand appearance during the hoteljacking incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:47.20,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,the world's attention has been on the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:51.64,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,The Order of the Black Knights, based on Zero's proclamation, are allies of the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:57.05,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Terrorists who get civilians involved, tyrannical troops, corrupt politicians,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:59.69,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,enterprises that are only concerned with making money, criminal organizations, etc...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:02.50,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,We've eliminated those who can't be punished by law.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:07.18,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,We quickly became heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:11.62,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Our supporters increased and we came into possession of Knightmares again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.47,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, not everything goes our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:15.86,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:18.27,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this Order of the Black Knights nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:19.57,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:22.23,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,We can't say anything bad about Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.94,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,We're Elevens after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:28.09,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Our leader, Zero, killed Clovis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:31.49,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of people among our allies who wish to see his real face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.12,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:37.41,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,However, I feel that he would disappear if we forced him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:42.25,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,We probably can't do without him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:43.80,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:46.48,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been hanging out with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:47.88,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:49.67,Default,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.38,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:04.42,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the masses supporting the ones who rescued Euphemia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:08.70,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Even Kyoto is saying that they'll give the Guren Mk. II to the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:10.20,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,To that half-assed group?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:13.94,Default,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Those people aren't even a resistance. Their killing of Colonel Kusakabe proves that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:16.30,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,The Colonel committed suicide, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.53,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,There were rumors that they couldn't stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:21.66,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Toudou, if we do nothing and this goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:28.75,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress Kallen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.11,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress Kallen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:32.94,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,President?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:34.76,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:35.45,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:39.42,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I take her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:40.79,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,To the guest room, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:42.01,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,To my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.19,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:44.50,Default,Stepmother,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:47.64,Default,Stepmother,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would be a guy when she said it was your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:49.79,Default,Stepmother,0000,0000,0000,,Coming home in the morning and not going to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:51.82,Default,Stepmother,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you've been going in and out of the ghetto as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:54.90,Default,Stepmother,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing all these wonderful things while your father is off working in the motherland...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.07,Default,Stepmother,0000,0000,0000,,Blood cannot be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:02.28,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who is really enjoying father's absence, aren't you?{the wicked stepmom is having an affair, LOLOL}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:08.67,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:11.02,Default,Stepmother,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:13.62,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Madam, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.51,Default,Stepmother,0000,0000,0000,,You're so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:17.67,Default,Stepmother,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing going for you is that you're a female.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.53,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it's a complicated family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:23.90,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to give me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.06,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather asked me to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:26.98,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,The Principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.89,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Your grades since junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.94,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,He thought it would be inappropriate to give this to you at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:36.28,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's been exposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:40.70,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,That I'm half Britannian and half Eleven.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.49,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,The one earlier was my stepmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:48.62,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,My real mother is that dimwitted maid who knocked over the vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:53.96,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is the head of the Stadtfeld family?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.34,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,My mother is an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:10:58.42,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, she's being ordered around as a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:04.50,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,She can't do any significant work, so no matter how much she's being looked down at, she has no choice but to smile weakly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.64,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,There's obviously no reason for her to stay in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:11.11,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,It's thick-skinned of her to stay in the residence of her former lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:13.40,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:15.56,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I just find her troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:17.87,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this sure is a deep story.{moar liek, "well this sounds like an episode of jerry springer"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:21.64,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,The legal wife, the adulteress, and her daughter are all living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.20,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.91,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Daily life isn't inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:28.39,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,It's not... something unbearable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:29.87,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:37.75,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can bear with them alone, if they pile up, you might collapse under them someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:40.24,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:44.34,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I like to know the secrets of others, I don't like to leak them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:04.71,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty embarassing, isn't it? Crying over a situation like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:06.19,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me sentimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:11.69,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But, it was nice that everyone got rescued by those people from the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:18.38,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,If they wanted to capture the culprits, they should've waited for the police to go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:20.33,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.70,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,They must have thought that the police were incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:25.54,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The police...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:29.26,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they're incompetent now, it's okay as long as they start to change internally, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:34.10,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,They intend to change, but end up being tied down by various hindrances.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:38.27,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That's something you should say only after they put in all of their effort and try to make changes up until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:41.36,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,By not doing that, they're just self-justifying their actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:42.86,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Self-justifying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.89,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,What is this evil they speak of?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:47.80,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what they're basing it upon, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:50.33,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,They're just helping themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:54.31,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? It's just you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:59.33,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I need to get back to the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:00.71,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Shirley.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:01.55,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:03.26,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.52,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:18.09,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Some time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:21.51,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,When you're free, how about going with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:24.07,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he needs to return to the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:29.20,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Return... Is that where you belong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:30.92,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Refrain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:31.85,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a narcotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:34.65,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,It allows the user to feel as if he or she has returned to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:37.21,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like it would sell well, especially to the Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:41.63,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone gets nostalgic about Japan before she was conquered by Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:46.86,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a drug targeted at the Japanese. We can't leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:50.73,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start to act once their illegally obtained supplies arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:54.76,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Our resources have increased and there are a lot of people who want to be our comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.10,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,The Order of the Black Knights is pretty popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.44,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,That's because we are the allies of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.64,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you again once the ammunition arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:06.03,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,You, Eleven, try and say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.81,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize, dammit. Apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:10.42,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you Elevens great at lowering your heads?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:11.09,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Eleven...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:15.16,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:17.62,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There are five of them. You can't win, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:19.78,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Then I should leave him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:22.08,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look at the Eleven who's being harassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.38,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and try to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:30.76,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, that Eleven won't be able to do business here tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:33.93,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,He has chosen to be a Britannian slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:37.22,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to work in the settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:38.29,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:40.38,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.33,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the Elevens are pitiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:45.34,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,You can't possibly want to be their friends, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.26,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,How could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:51.87,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You guys should be bored of it, right? Bullying the Elevens...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:57.70,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:58.89,Default,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the game center.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:00.00,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,I'm broke though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.95,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they're the kind of people who get bored easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:06.96,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:09.17,Default,Vendor,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:11.07,Default,Vendor,0000,0000,0000,,A Britannian student...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:13.35,Default,Vendor,0000,0000,0000,,W-Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:15.49,Default,Vendor,0000,0000,0000,,W-Want a Californian hot dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:18.33,Default,Vendor,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is he your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:19.76,Default,Vendor,0000,0000,0000,,If it's okay, will the two of you please come this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:22.19,Default,Vendor,0000,0000,0000,,There's ice cream too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:27.23,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Area 11 can be said to be much better now, compared to when it was still Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:32.83,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to her becoming a colonized Area of Britannia, both the military and the economy have stabilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:34.70,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Citizenship can be obtained too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:39.24,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,They just need to do some paperwork at the public office, and they can become an honorary Britannian, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:41.44,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing left is the issue of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:44.37,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I understand why they would want to treasure that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:45.91,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:46.65,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:50.61,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what you've said so far, but what do you, Lelouch Lamperouge, really think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:51.96,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:52.95,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:57.30,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,You seem smart, but you're all talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:16:02.48,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley is always complaining, "Lulu doesn't put in any effort. It's such a waste of his brilliant mind."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:04.10,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:07.51,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You should understand from the incident with that Eleven earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:10.86,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to live by lowering your head to the Britannians.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:21.10,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,You think that's cool? Embracing those ideas and looking down upon the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:25.29,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,It was stupid of me to hope for anything out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.77,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you were a decent man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:39.68,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Concerning the Orange incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:41.87,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:48.14,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Concerning the Kururugi Suzaku escape incident, is it true that you have no recollection of that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:50.14,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I don't expect you to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:55.57,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,No. The truth is that during the Shinjuku incident, I also experienced memory loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:56.78,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:17:00.42,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,When I regained consciousness, my Sutherland had been stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:05.16,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that I can recall happening before the memory loss was meeting a young man in a school uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:06.91,Default,Jerimiah,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to that student?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:11.58,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember his face, but I think this is worth investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:15.28,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,What is that Zero thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:20.53,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he wanted to defeat Britannia, but the things we're doing are no different from the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:23.54,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't feel bad to be thanked by people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:26.23,Default,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup. We're heroes on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:29.81,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,This is the right thing for us to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:31.19,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Kallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:35.03,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,It's Zero's signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:37.01,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,He did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:39.53,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Time after time, I wonder what trick he uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:46.66,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Is the distribution for Nagoya complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.50,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe since it's inside a settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:54.92,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,The Order of the Black Knights has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:56.84,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:00.05,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,A Knightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:00.66,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.85,Default,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:07.93,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,The Knightmare is indeed amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:09.44,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,There's an overwhelming advantage in just having one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:19.32,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Japan! Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.46,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm getting married next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.81,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,I've been promoted. I'll be going to Paris this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:25.79,Default,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go watch the fireworks together next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:29.00,Default,???05,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me. Japanese technology is the best in the world, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:30.11,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Refrain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:33.45,Default,Vendor,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided! I'm going to study abroad! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:37.81,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If they pile up, you might collapse under them someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.68,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. That's why I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.30,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! It's not safe to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.20,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:58.73,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Naoto, you need to pay attention to what Kallen is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:02.31,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a weak woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:06.35,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on Britannia, depending on men, and now drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.17,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Brother isn't here anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:08.87,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,If this goes on...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:14.25,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,The night police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:18.93,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:20.10,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Have they teamed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:20.71,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:21.97,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.92,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure when I investigated...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:25.24,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,God dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.32,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,What a nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:42.05,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:43.77,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I don't want her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:46.41,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I don't want her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:56.13,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Kallen... Naoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:06.60,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If my opponent is in a Knigtmare, then I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.31,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,R... un...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:16.40,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Run, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:18.07,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:22.22,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be with you, Kallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:23.45,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:27.91,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,That was why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:30.64,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,That was why you continued to stay in that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:32.18,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Just for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:33.74,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:45.15,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... the idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:20:59.86,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Kallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.51,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,That was great, Kallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:11.11,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,You can become a Britannian.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:14.37,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, you won't be bullied anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:17.93,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,You can even make phone calls and travel as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:21.09,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's... her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:25.55,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,False tears are capable of hurting other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:28.68,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,False smiles are capable of hurting one's self.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:34.92,Default,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,It's the aftereffects of the drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:36.48,Default,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,She can barely talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:39.90,Default,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take time for her to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:43.21,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,The verdict is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:45.01,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,It's twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:49.03,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:52.33,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, I'll change the world before you're released.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:56.25,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Mother and I will live together in a normal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:58.53,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,So... So...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:03.46,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Do... your... best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:06.68,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Kallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:08.91,Default,Kallen's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:16.73,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll do my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:23.86,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I will do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.55,0:23:57.74,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Memories of the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.10,0:24:00.36,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,People who are able to reminisce about it are blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.74,0:24:02.92,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,They think that tomorrow will really come.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.57,0:24:06.79,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But who can promise that it will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.23,0:24:10.66,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right to believe in her if Kallen wishes to get into it.{I'm pretty sure "it" refers to Kallen piloting the Guren}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.02,0:24:14.57,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because we have no choice but to live for the present.
